      <body>
         <div type="page" xml:id="pg_04"></div>
         <cbml:panel n="1" characters = "#jon #liz">
            <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#jon">
               Sigh.
            </cbml:balloon>
            <note type="panelDesc">Jon is sighing happily as he looks at Liz.</note>
         </cbml:panel>
         <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#jon #liz">
            <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#jon">
               Sigh.
            </cbml:balloon>
            <note type="panelDesc"> Jon is still sighing and staring at Liz. Liz looks concerned.</note>
         </cbml:panel>
         <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#jon #liz #garfield">
            <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#jon">
               Sigh.
            </cbml:balloon>
            <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#liz">
               Is he okay?
            </cbml:balloon>
            <cbml:balloon type="thought" who="#garfield">
               I'll get his inhaler.
            </cbml:balloon>
            <note type="panelDesc">
               Liz is feeling concerned about Jon, and she asks Garfield if Jon is okay because of his constant sighing and staring. Garfield leaves the room to get an inhaler.
            </note>
         </cbml:panel>
